Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.78,0:01:37.15,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's time, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.53,0:01:39.13,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd better head over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.89,0:01:49.17,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, who should be next?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.75,0:01:51.90,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I'll see what Kanade thinks.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.14,0:01:53.90,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.49,0:01:55.17,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hinata!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.40,0:01:56.62,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Otonashi{\fnNyala}-{\fn}san.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.94,0:01:57.68,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Naoi?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.40,0:02:01.61,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.61,0:02:03.86,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Same to you, where did you crawl out from?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.44,0:02:07.48,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So... did you two have some business with me? {both at once}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.48,0:02:11.03,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh that's right! Where are you going, Otonashi?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.00,0:02:13.50,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter where he's going!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.51,0:02:14.98,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This has nothing to do with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.18,0:02:20.10,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to talk to Otonashi so I can help out with what he's trying to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.46,0:02:23.49,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That should be my role.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.49,0:02:24.70,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're just in the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.19,0:02:27.03,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and vanish.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.40,0:02:31.92,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, look into my eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.38,0:02:34.32,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You are toilet paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.71,0:02:38.55,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You will realize the splendor of how easily toilet paper is flushed—
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.55,0:02:39.95,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.66,0:02:42.93,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Hinata!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.27,0:02:45.26,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Please allow me to assist you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.59,0:02:49.10,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you guys understand what I'm trying to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.10,0:02:50.26,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.65,0:02:52.19,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.63,0:02:54.81,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're erasing everyone one by one, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.81,0:02:57.44,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It sounds evil when you say it...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.44,0:03:02.52,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway Naoi, shouldn't you be free of regrets at this point?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.52,0:03:04.47,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to be together with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.47,0:03:07.68,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And I don't want to disappear before this guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.68,0:03:10.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't stay for such a petty reason!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.00,0:03:11.86,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.86,0:03:13.07,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.07,0:03:14.72,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't asking you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.25,0:03:17.86,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on Otonashi{\fnNyala}-{\fn}san, you need a partner, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.70,0:03:21.51,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Make use of me, Otonashi{\fnNyala}-{\fn}san!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.86,0:03:24.02,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Is something wrong? {yeah, maybe it's the fact your shadow is A MONSTER}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.19,0:03:27.15,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.41,0:03:28.68,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you do something again?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.09,0:03:30.31,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.48,0:03:31.56,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't done anyth—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.25,0:03:35.04,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.04,0:03:36.74,main,,0000,0000,0000,,An enemy? Do we shoot it??
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.16,0:03:39.02,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's entering me...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.67,0:03:41.02,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Something is entering me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.02,0:03:41.82,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Otonashi{\fnNyala}-{\fn}san!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.82,0:03:42.61,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.04,0:03:50.77,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hinata!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.58,0:03:54.33,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Will this thing even die?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.81,0:04:03.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Did we get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.32,0:04:06.59,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.95,0:04:12.55,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hinata{\fnNyala}-{\fn}san and Otonashi{\fnNyala}-{\fn}san confronted and defeated a second one.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.55,0:04:14.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody was harmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.88,0:04:16.95,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So a second one appeared...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.95,0:04:20.70,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The natural assumption is that this is some new skill Angel came up with, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.70,0:04:21.99,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Something doesn't feel right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.37,0:04:23.39,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.27,0:04:27.60,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Relay this to all Battlefront members.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.60,0:04:29.32,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Henceforth, it is forbidden to move solo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.70,0:04:31.91,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay in groups of at least two.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.50,0:04:35.47,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll treat the shadow as a separate enemy from Angel.{敵性勢力}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.27,0:04:38.46,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Be sure to stay on full alert at all times.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.95,0:04:40.08,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Acknowledged.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.53,0:04:41.84,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What now, Yurippe{\fnNyala}-{\fn}san?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.84,0:04:45.19,main,,0000,0000,0000,,"Yurippe{\fnNyala}-{\fn}san" will think through all the possibilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,< sign : Incinerator >
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.71,0:04:51.60,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Student Council President Tachibana Kanade{\fnNyala}-{\fn}san,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.60,0:04:54.12,main,,0000,0000,0000,,please come to the student council office immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.12,0:04:55.56,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I repeat...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.11,0:04:54.20,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that Yurippe's voice?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.20,0:04:55.56,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.56,0:04:59.16,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad, she might find out about what we're doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.31,0:05:00.60,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That would be bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.10,0:05:02.02,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.02,0:05:02.73,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.70,0:05:07.11,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you guys here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.56,0:05:09.08,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Allow us to sit in on this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.08,0:05:13.63,main,,0000,0000,0000,,As the former acting student council president and current vice{\fnNyala}-{\fn}president, I gave him permission.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.63,0:05:15.38,main,,0000,0000,0000,,How is this your jurisdiction?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.73,0:05:17.37,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the student council office.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.16,0:05:20.05,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.67,0:05:24.38,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So what's with this shadow?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.74,0:05:25.51,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.09,0:05:28.18,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you program it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.48,0:05:29.18,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.60,0:05:32.22,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Then there's a chance it's a bug. {wtf... this world really is an RPG? lol}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.22,0:05:34.33,main,,0000,0000,0000,,When did you last write a program?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.33,0:05:35.43,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The day before yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.43,0:05:37.81,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The timing fits...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.81,0:05:40.02,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be intruding on your room, is that okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.81,0:05:43.36,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm leaving it to you, Takeyama{\fnNyala}-{\fn}kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.36,0:05:44.17,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.17,0:05:45.14,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And call me Chri—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.24,0:05:47.04,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what kind of program was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.04,0:05:47.95,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wings.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.95,0:05:48.76,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wings?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.76,0:05:50.08,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You added wings?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.08,0:05:51.28,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So you can fly?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.51,0:05:53.05,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's a decoration.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.06,0:05:54.81,main,,0000,0000,0000,,A decoration?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.10,0:05:56.61,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, a decoration.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.61,0:05:57.41,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.68,0:06:00.27,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I was told it would be more angel{\fnNyala}-{\fn}like.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.27,0:06:00.94,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You were told?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.24,0:06:02.46,main,,0000,0000,0000,,By who?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.55,0:06:04.37,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.37,0:06:05.92,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That was me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.75,0:06:09.21,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I believed it would give her more impact as the president,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.21,0:06:14.30,main,,0000,0000,0000,,so in my position as the former acting president and current vice{\fnNyala}-{\fn}president, I made the suggestion to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.30,0:06:17.06,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If the student council president had wings, she'd have more impact?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.29,0:06:18.08,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.08,0:06:19.23,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I believed that for the president,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.40,0:06:20.06,main,,0000,0000,0000,,wings
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.35,0:06:21.56,main,,0000,0000,0000,,would be suitable.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.55,0:06:28.35,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.76,0:06:31.44,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're surprisingly obedient though.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.44,0:06:33.73,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't sense one bit of cruelty in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.05,0:06:36.39,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You seem like the way you always were.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.39,0:06:37.85,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No, she is cruel.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.85,0:06:40.46,main,,0000,0000,0000,,As the vice{\fnNyala}-{\fn}president, I get stabbed everyday.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.46,0:06:41.89,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Er... why?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.89,0:06:45.30,main,,0000,0000,0000,,When she's in a bad mood, she stabs anyone nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.30,0:06:49.61,main,,0000,0000,0000,,In my position as vice{\fnNyala}-{\fn}president, I am often near her, so I get stabbed quite a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.61,0:06:52.42,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Just this morning, she stabbed me till my guts were hanging out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.10,0:06:55.88,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Though, it appears she's in a very good mood right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.93,0:06:58.70,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.89,0:07:01.81,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.81,0:07:02.77,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Please respond.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.80,0:07:05.73,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Takeyama{\fnNyala}-{\fn}kun? How was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,{sign: Girls Dormitory {\fnNyala}-{\fn} Angel area}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.20,0:07:08.24,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't find any bugs.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.24,0:07:12.36,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I looked into the most recent program, but it's a simple decorative program.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.95,0:07:16.49,main,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way a bug that might have its own will and attacks people could come from this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.29,0:07:18.90,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And call me Chri—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.90,0:07:20.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What about the other programs?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.93,0:07:24.38,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Passive, Overdrive, Active, and Hand Sonic.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.94,0:07:28.30,main,,0000,0000,0000,,They're all programs from before, though there are minor changes to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.30,0:07:29.01,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.31,0:07:32.80,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Is she going to make him erase them?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.80,0:07:34.89,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We'd have to start from fresh...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.77,0:07:38.04,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, did you just hear gunfire?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.11,0:07:40.85,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about? What gunfire?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.99,0:07:42.82,main,,0000,0000,0000,,From outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.53,0:07:47.51,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.01,0:07:49.55,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Those monsters!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.70,0:07:51.32,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are there so many?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.26,0:07:53.46,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanade, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.60,0:08:10.26,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yurippe!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.25,0:08:16.50,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.50,0:08:17.51,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.51,0:08:18.37,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.37,0:08:19.45,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Otonashi{\fnNyala}-{\fn}san!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.27,0:08:30.29,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay Yuri?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.29,0:08:31.35,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Otonashi{\fnNyala}-{\fn}kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.35,0:08:32.54,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to keep you waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.06,0:08:33.99,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Bow before me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.83,0:08:36.11,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need backup!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.11,0:08:37.99,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, don't say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.25,0:08:45.59,main,,0000,0000,0000,,How shallow{\fnNyala}-{\fn}minded.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.15,0:08:48.60,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Woah! Dancing in the shadow!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.77,0:08:55.22,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I kiss you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.69,0:09:09.36,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't want to be on the receiving end of that...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.39,0:09:15.45,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are you trying to cut your own team?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.91,0:09:17.05,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's in the plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.05,0:09:18.70,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't put that in the plan! Leave it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.70,0:09:20.88,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop messing about and help out!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.37,0:09:27.40,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That was...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.91,0:09:35.69,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Is everyone alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.68,0:09:39.67,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What were those? Monsters?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.67,0:09:41.49,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What were those creepy things?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.49,0:09:43.51,main,,0000,0000,0000,,They weren't in this world before.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.80,0:09:45.49,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this a nightmare?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.49,0:09:47.67,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a carnival and everyone's invited.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.67,0:09:50.53,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Did we stay in this world for too long?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.53,0:09:51.52,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.52,0:09:53.46,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You get this in games, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.46,0:09:56.80,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Invincible monsters that appear to prevent infinite play time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.80,0:09:58.09,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.63,0:09:59.53,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously though...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.40,0:10:01.89,main,,0000,0000,0000,,She's just like an ally.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.69,0:10:05.06,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! hey!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.29,0:10:06.24,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Fujimaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.46,0:10:08.67,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.67,0:10:10.05,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Takamatsu...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.11,0:10:13.45,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Takamatsu got done in!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,{Study Block {\fnNyala}-{\fn} Connecting Corridor}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.25,0:10:23.77,main,,0000,0000,0000,,His glasses...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.16,0:10:26.21,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw it...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.21,0:10:28.55,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw that shadow eating him!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.55,0:10:29.85,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Eating?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.31,0:10:35.01,main,,0000,0000,0000,,When I ran into him, his whole body was already covered by the shadow...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.53,0:10:37.68,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I tried to save him!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.05,0:10:40.14,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But I couldn't do anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.73,0:10:43.59,main,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, his glasses fell off...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.59,0:10:45.71,main,,0000,0000,0000,,For him to leave behind his glasses...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.71,0:10:47.14,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.14,0:10:47.98,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And then?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.98,0:10:50.98,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The ground absorbed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.98,0:10:51.78,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The ground?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.33,0:10:53.50,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is too irregular.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.61,0:10:55.63,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.25,0:10:59.30,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Some other will besides ours is at work here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.92,0:11:02.01,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What on earth's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.90,0:11:07.98,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Takamatsu's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.92,0:11:10.05,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Takamatsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,<sign: Study Block A {\fnNyala}-{\fn} Classroom >
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.60,0:11:11.84,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think you're doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.84,0:11:13.49,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone was worried about you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.23,0:11:15.24,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Worried?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.84,0:11:16.79,main,,0000,0000,0000,,About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.79,0:11:18.15,main,,0000,0000,0000,,"About what"?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.15,0:11:20.70,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You were eaten by the shadow, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.24,0:11:23.65,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't understand what you're talking about...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.65,0:11:26.12,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't realize it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.12,0:11:27.96,main,,0000,0000,0000,,A shadow ate you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.96,0:11:30.66,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And then you were swallowed by the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.96,0:11:32.56,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened after that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.56,0:11:33.88,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure what you mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.30,0:11:37.71,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I woke up in the dorms and headed to school as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.71,0:11:39.56,main,,0000,0000,0000,,To school?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.56,0:11:42.60,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You put on that uniform and came here to attend classes?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.60,0:11:43.64,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.64,0:11:45.93,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to disappear! Don't you get that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.55,0:11:47.40,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Disappear?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.91,0:11:49.55,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What will?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.13,0:11:54.01,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This looks bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.01,0:11:55.92,main,,0000,0000,0000,,He's become strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.92,0:11:57.86,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, he was always strange, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.62,0:11:59.48,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Takamatsu...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.48,0:12:01.25,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough, Hinata{\fnNyala}-{\fn}kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.25,0:12:02.90,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean "enough"?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.90,0:12:05.01,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, but you're interfering with my class.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.01,0:12:06.19,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.19,0:12:07.77,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We're just going to leave him?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.77,0:12:08.89,main,,0000,0000,0000,,He'll disappear!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.89,0:12:09.98,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I said let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.87,0:12:12.69,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oyama{\fnNyala}-{\fn}kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,< sign: Study Block A {\fnNyala}-{\fn} Stairway >
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.80,0:12:22.25,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That conversation just now was enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.25,0:12:24.20,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I know what's happening now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.02,0:12:26.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,He...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.29,0:12:27.97,main,,0000,0000,0000,,...has become an NPC.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.47,0:12:31.38,main,,0000,0000,0000,,W{\fnNyala}-{\fn}Wait a second...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.38,0:12:33.11,main,,0000,0000,0000,,How could that be?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.11,0:12:34.25,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't get it at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.25,0:12:37.44,main,,0000,0000,0000,,By NPC, you mean he doesn't have a soul?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.44,0:12:40.23,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Then where did his soul go?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.62,0:12:42.77,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It was eaten.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.77,0:12:45.13,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.13,0:12:51.26,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying he can't disappear anymore, and is doomed to take classes for eternity?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.26,0:12:53.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's how it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.20,0:12:54.47,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.47,0:12:57.15,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's worse than death...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.15,0:13:01.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,To be stuck in this place for eternity...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.00,0:13:02.25,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.60,0:13:03.64,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.51,0:13:05.70,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's terrible...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.29,0:13:11.49,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So this kind of thing is possible in this world...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.91,0:13:15.61,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Being erased by Angel would be better than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.61,0:13:18.65,main,,0000,0000,0000,,On top of that, it seems that the shadows are multiplying.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.65,0:13:20.66,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What are we supposed to do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.66,0:13:21.47,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yurippe!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,< sign: Gymnasium >
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.09,0:13:34.90,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This world is developing an abnormality —
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.90,0:13:37.38,main,,0000,0000,0000,,the arrival of an opponent other than Angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.38,0:13:39.62,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not very imaginative, but we're calling it "shadow".
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.05,0:13:44.33,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Unlike Angel, it appears and vanishes without warning, and attacks indiscriminately.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.45,0:13:51.29,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyone who gets eaten by the shadow loses their soul and turns into a normal NPC who attends classes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.29,0:13:53.94,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It is currently multiplying in unlimited numbers.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.94,0:13:55.15,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Its origin is unknown,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.15,0:13:57.51,main,,0000,0000,0000,,and we don't have any countermeasures.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.51,0:14:02.88,main,,0000,0000,0000,,As I had Yusa{\fnNyala}-{\fn}san broadcast, the only way to defend ourselves is to move as a group.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.37,0:14:06.48,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, even while we face this danger,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.84,0:14:13.95,main,,0000,0000,0000,,some individuals within the Afterlife Battlefront have formed new ideals and are trying to take us in a new direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.95,0:14:19.92,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That path could be a viable choice to avoid the danger we are currently facing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.92,0:14:24.26,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore, as their representative, Otonashi{\fnNyala}-{\fn}kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.26,0:14:27.08,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Can we hear your point of view on that, straight up in front of everyone here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.60,0:14:32.01,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems she found out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.01,0:14:33.04,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.36,0:14:55.12,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't screw with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.46,0:14:56.89,main,,0000,0000,0000,,How can you say that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.89,0:14:59.07,main,,0000,0000,0000,,There’s no way it can be that convenient!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.07,0:14:59.87,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.87,0:15:01.86,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Like hell there’s a choice like that in this world!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.86,0:15:03.25,main,,0000,0000,0000,,There is.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.29,0:15:07.29,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yui found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.43,0:15:12.26,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Even someone like me, who died like human trash...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.00,0:15:15.97,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Even I was able to grant that to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.74,0:15:17.94,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.07,0:15:20.49,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I may be God,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.61,0:15:27.78,main,,0000,0000,0000,,but even so, Otonashi restored my human soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.31,0:15:30.16,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Just by saying one thing to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.90,0:15:32.49,main,,0000,0000,0000,,by encouraging me.{with encouraging words?}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.55,0:15:36.59,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It is up to each one of you which road you take.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.08,0:15:37.96,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.42,0:15:39.78,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What'll you do, Yurippe?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.99,0:15:41.16,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.16,0:15:43.62,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm always doing my own thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.62,0:15:45.54,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't be protecting you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.05,0:15:48.21,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I just do whatever I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.50,0:15:55.07,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Time is running out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.07,0:15:57.01,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Think carefully about it for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.46,0:15:58.44,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.44,0:15:59.30,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Dismissed!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.65,0:16:02.84,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Got a moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.37,0:16:07.65,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Yuri?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.20,0:16:10.95,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Get her to intercept the shadow.{or is it be bait for an ambush?}{迎撃 doesn't mean ambush in any context}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.95,0:16:12.06,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanade?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.06,0:16:12.76,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.76,0:16:18.09,main,,0000,0000,0000,,She's more useful fighting without thinking, rather than pondering over a plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.09,0:16:19.34,main,,0000,0000,0000,,From what I've seen, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.56,0:16:22.33,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You were watching us?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.56,0:16:25.80,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess we can’t fool Yurippe.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.80,0:16:28.66,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But Kanade's our friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.66,0:16:29.80,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We should do it together.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.20,0:16:33.47,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The other members are also your companions.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.47,0:16:36.51,main,,0000,0000,0000,,To protect them, we'll need her power...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.13,0:16:42.25,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That overwhelming power that she's been fighting against the Battlefront with for so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.86,0:16:46.11,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess only an angel can stand up to that thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.11,0:16:48.42,main,,0000,0000,0000,,She's not an angel, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.92,0:16:50.69,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.69,0:16:51.82,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.82,0:16:53.70,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I said she's not an angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.28,0:16:56.39,main,,0000,0000,0000,,She's a human, like us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.39,0:16:57.91,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you notice?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.95,0:17:03.24,main,,0000,0000,0000,,As God, I knew all along.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.24,0:17:04.91,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're seriously disturbed...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.27,0:17:07.71,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, you aren't an angel?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.99,0:17:11.10,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not an angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.10,0:17:14.60,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I gave you the same answer when we first met.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.30,0:17:18.52,main,,0000,0000,0000,,They said you were an angel or something...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.14,0:17:21.60,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not an angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.62,0:17:23.76,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.76,0:17:25.56,main,,0000,0000,0000,,A lot's happened since then...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.56,0:17:27.31,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's because of you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.31,0:17:29.49,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So why is Kanade here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.49,0:17:31.94,main,,0000,0000,0000,,She's the student council president, so why hasn't she disappeared?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.17,0:17:35.45,main,,0000,0000,0000,,She has a reason to be here, obviously.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.89,0:17:38.24,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.54,0:17:42.86,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're carrying some burden, just like us?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.75,0:17:46.09,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess we'll have to lift that off you too,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.09,0:17:46.76,main,,0000,0000,0000,,right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.40,0:17:51.64,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So Yuri,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.64,0:17:53.08,main,,0000,0000,0000,,what'll you do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.08,0:17:55.10,main,,0000,0000,0000,,There's something I want to check.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.10,0:17:56.87,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to fight the shadow?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.87,0:17:57.77,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Depending on how it turns out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.07,0:17:59.26,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too dangerous alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.80,0:18:01.61,main,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.61,0:18:04.39,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I gave everyone the freedom to choose what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.75,0:18:06.89,main,,0000,0000,0000,,There are people who will follow you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.89,0:18:09.26,main,,0000,0000,0000,,They need time to think.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.26,0:18:10.90,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an important decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.90,0:18:13.61,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's... true.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.61,0:18:18.78,main,,0000,0000,0000,,When I return, if everyone's gone and safely left this world,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.78,0:18:21.42,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll assume you managed to send them all off.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.42,0:18:22.59,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.59,0:18:23.48,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll wait for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.93,0:18:24.98,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be dumb.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.98,0:18:28.13,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If you wait alone, the shadow will get you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.13,0:18:32.12,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You need to get out of this world before that happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.69,0:18:34.43,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.82,0:18:36.40,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No, we'll worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.40,0:18:37.26,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hinata{\fnNyala}-{\fn}kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.62,0:18:39.35,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying, all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.92,0:18:42.35,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't we form this Battlefront together?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.91,0:18:45.64,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We've spent a long time here together,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.91,0:18:48.16,main,,0000,0000,0000,,so we'll leave together too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.16,0:18:50.13,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't leave you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.84,0:18:52.91,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're such an idiot, like always.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.27,0:18:56.07,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing's going to be solved with emotional speeches.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.66,0:18:57.60,main,,0000,0000,0000,,An attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.60,0:18:58.70,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We're under attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.93,0:19:01.32,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanade{\fnNyala}-{\fn}chan, I'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.78,0:19:03.64,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hand Sonic, version 5.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.45,0:19:10.33,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if we can, we'll meet again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.33,0:19:11.29,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yurippe!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.28,0:19:16.38,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What a terrible nickname.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.20,0:19:20.72,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But it might have been why everyone followed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.59,0:19:22.71,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.38,0:20:50.26,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! I guess this is the last one.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.01,0:21:05.46,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That transformation...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.65,0:21:15.60,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If it’s possible for NPCs to be reprogrammed, like Kanade does to herself...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.37,0:21:23.70,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That software must be being used to transform the NPCs and attack us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.70,0:21:30.03,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And there must be a whole load of computers wherever that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.35,0:21:33.44,main,,0000,0000,0000,,There has to be a large number of computers wherever that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.91,0:21:36.94,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's the case, there can be only one place.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,< sign: Library >
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,< sign: PC Room 1 >
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,< sign: Library Interior {\fnNyala}-{\fn} PC Room 1 >
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.88,0:21:55.24,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Checkmate.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.25,0:21:56.37,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Put up your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.49,0:22:00.85,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you checkmate?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.85,0:22:02.80,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you play chess?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.07,0:22:04.46,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the culprit?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.41,0:22:12.57,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So in this age of computers, people still play with those?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.57,0:22:15.68,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You have a good hobby for such a young person.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.91,0:22:16.85,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.41,0:22:19.30,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm? Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.30,0:22:20.59,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What were you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.91,0:22:21.85,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Here?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.15,0:22:23.04,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.04,0:22:25.73,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Setting up new computers.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.73,0:22:26.89,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What for?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.22,0:22:30.96,main,,0000,0000,0000,,They have good specs, so they get stolen.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.96,0:22:33.50,main,,0000,0000,0000,,When there's not enough we have to replace them.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.72,0:22:35.33,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Any leads on the culprit?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.33,0:22:37.70,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing at this stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.92,0:22:41.28,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that all?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.18,0:22:43.13,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.67,0:22:45.32,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for stopping you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.43,0:23:08.66,main,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no doubt about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.12,0:23:12.95,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The one stealing the computers is currently playing God of this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.89,0:23:18.24,main,,0000,0000,0000,,He's using the stolen computers to interfere with the NPCs.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.85,0:23:20.69,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But how do I catch him?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.80,0:23:23.78,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have the time to relax and think.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.98,0:23:26.04,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Even now, the shadows are multiplying.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.94,0:23:30.78,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And these aren't exactly easy to just make off with.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.49,0:23:35.82,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Does he sneak in at night, put them on a cart, then take them out?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.11,0:23:37.77,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Or does he use a window?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.41,0:23:59.03,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Found you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.50,0:24:06.30,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.30,0:24:07.28,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.85,0:24:12.84,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Guild again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,< preview >
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.01,0:24:18.08,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We're breaking through!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.69,0:24:19.70,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with this world?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.58,0:24:20.43,main,,0000,0000,0000,,"I wonder if we can surprise God"??
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.43,0:24:21.40,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Disappear!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.41,0:24:23.19,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Because it doesn't seem anyone would notice if I disappeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.60,0:24:24.91,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I only move to save Yurippe!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.56,0:24:25.84,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Disappear like miserable toilet paper!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.98,0:24:25.64,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Think of it like it's gained the fighting strength of 100 people.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.87,0:24:24.29,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll also play in a band in the next life!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.64,0:24:25.66,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me your hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.78,0:24:25.67,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You've done well to reach here.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.67,0:24:28.96,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If I disappear now... can I start over?
